articles.title: Google Maps Street View: Hiker's horrifying accident seen in grisly shot - what happened? - Express
articles.description: GOOGLE Maps Street View has become well known for capturing shots that disturb, entertain and confuse. People are often snapped in these eye-catching scenes as they go about their lives - such as this one man in Europe.
